snippet.title: Juno | New Hero Gameplay Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
3, 2, 1, blast off with our newest Support hero, Juno!

Armed with her versatile Mediblaster and Pulsar Torpedoes, Juno provides simultaneous healing and damage in support of her team.

Play as Juno for a limited-time July 19 through July 21 until her official launch in Season 12 on Aug 20.

—
Juno is equipped with Pulsar Torpedoes that can lock onto multiple targets. Her Glide Boost ability allows her to swiftly maneuver the battlefield to provide critical support wherever she’s needed. Juno's Hyper Ring propels the team into action, while her Ultimate Orbital Ray boosts damage and replenishes health.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
